<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF696AD6F8319F2A174EB100" pageId="146" pageNumber="907" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF696AD6F8319F2A174EB100" blockId="146.[1993,2590,2261,2688]" pageId="146" pageNumber="907">
Limited genetic data place this species within 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF696AD6F80D9FFB1655B289" authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1842" box="[2033,2133,2466,2491]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="146" pageNumber="907" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Murina</taxonomicName>
, close to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF696AD6F72A9FFB1775B289" authorityName="Csorba &amp; Bates" authorityYear="2005" box="[2262,2421,2466,2491]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="146" pageNumber="913" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="harrisoni">M. harrisoni</taxonomicName>
, M. hutton, and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF696AD6F7F59F9B16BDB2D1" authorityName="Ogneyv" authorityYear="1913" box="[2057,2237,2498,2531]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="146" pageNumber="913" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="ussuriensis">M. ussuriensis</taxonomicName>
, making 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF696AD6F6C79F9B179FB2D1" authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1842" box="[2363,2463,2498,2531]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="146" pageNumber="907" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Murina</taxonomicName>
paraphyletic and calling the generic validity of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF696AD6F61E9FB0160AB100" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1915" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Harpiola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="146" pageNumber="907" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Harpiola</taxonomicName>
into doubt. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
